Ability to add the weight/ marks allocated for assignments/ quizes etc in each module (as it depends on the module). So the student can see how much marks he had gained for continuos assesemnts that will be added to the modules.
Ability to get a graphical analysis of his performaance in various modules and semesters
The weight of each module is shown, depending on the number of credits it has, so the student knows which modules to spend more time on.
